<P>1. This Appeal be heard and determined by the same division of this Court as the following two Appeals:
<P1>a. Court of Appeal File No. CA44250 between The Owners, Strata Plan LMS3905 as Respondent and Crystal Square Parking Corporation as Appellant (the &ldquo;Crystal Square Appeal&rdquo;), and</P1>
<P1>b. Court of Appeal File No. File No. CA44684between The Owners, Strata Plan NWS 3457 as Appellant and The Owners, Strata Plan LMS 1425 as Respondent (the &ldquo;Scottsdale Village Appeal&rdquo;).</P1></P>
<P>2. This Appeal, the Crystal Square Appeal and the Scottsdale Village Appeal shall be heard sequentially in an order to be agreed on between counsel for the parties to the three appeals or, failing such agreement in the order directed by this Court;</P>
<P>3. The parties to the Crystal Square Appeal and the Scottsdale Village Appeal may file consent orders in those two appeals to the same effect as the orders sought under 1 and 2 above.</P>
<P>AND TAKE NOTICE THAT in support of the application will be read the affidavit of Garth S. McAlister sworn on January 29, 2018.</P>
<P>The applicant anticipates that this application will be uncontested.</P>
<P>Dated: <UNDER>29 /Jan/2018</UNDER></P>
<P>&ellip35; Signature of lawyer for the Appellant</P>
<P>Garth McAlister</P>
<P>This application will take no more than 15 minutes to be heard.</P>
