<P1>1. this appeal be heard and determined by the same division of this Court as the appeal known as Court of Appeal file No. CA44250 <CASEREF><SOC>The Owners, Strata Plan LMS 3905 v. Crystal Square Parking Corporation</SOC></CASEREF> (the &ldquo;Crystal Square Appeal&rdquo;);</P1>
